title: #92Noon Vox In The Box! Boudreau/Chavous/Cullen/Fletcher/Florio/Russo/Sickman
description: #92Noon sends the Wild off to Winnipeg with a Vox In The Box show live from the penalty box at the X! Brandon Mileski co-hosts the first hour as Wild Head Coach Bruce Boudreau and Wild forward Matt Cullen stops by. ProFootballTalk's Mike Florio makes his regular appearance. Corey Chavous talks more football. Wild GM Chuck Fletcher joins PA before The Athletic's Michael Russo swings by to beg for Wild tickets!
